sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 👤 User
    participant Frontend as 🎨 Frontend
    participant API as 🔌 API Gateway
    participant Classify as 1️⃣ Classify Node
    participant Agent as 2️⃣ Agent Node
    participant Tools as 3️⃣ Tools Node
    participant Analyze as 4️⃣ Analyze Node
    participant DB as 💾 Database

    User->>Frontend: "What's my runway?"
    Frontend->>API: POST /agent/chat
    activate API
    
    API->>DB: Fetch company context
    DB-->>API: {cash, burn_rate, revenue}
    
    API->>Classify: Classify query
    activate Classify
    Classify-->>Classify: "What's my runway?" → "simple"
    Classify-->>API: query_type = "simple"
    deactivate Classify
    
    API->>Agent: Select LLM + invoke
    activate Agent
    Agent->>Agent: Load Qwen3 (fast model)
    Agent->>Agent: Build CFO system prompt
    Agent->>Agent: Bind 10 tools + invoke LLM
    Agent-->>API: AIMessage + tool_calls
    deactivate Agent
    
    API->>Tools: Execute tools
    activate Tools
    
    Tools->>DB: get_cash_balance()
    DB-->>Tools: {cash: 2350000}
    
    Tools->>DB: get_burn_rate()
    DB-->>Tools: {burn: 125000, breakdown}
    
    Tools->>Tools: get_runway() = 2350000 / 125000
    Tools-->>Tools: {runway: 18.8 months, zero_date}
    
    Tools-->>API: [ToolMessage, ToolMessage, ToolMessage]
    deactivate Tools
    
    API->>Analyze: Check errors
    activate Analyze
    Analyze-->>Analyze: error_count < 3 ✓
    Analyze-->>API: proceed
    deactivate Analyze
    
    API-->>Frontend: {response: "Your runway is 18.8 months...", timestamp}
    deactivate API
    
    Frontend-->>User: Display in ChatDrawer

    style User fill:#e1f5ff
    style Frontend fill:#fff3e0
    style API fill:#f3e5f5
    style Classify fill:#e8f5e9
    style Agent fill:#e8f5e9
    style Tools fill:#e8f5e9
    style Analyze fill:#e8f5e9
    style DB fill:#fce4ec
